19 Section 1354. There is hereby re-created, to continue until
20 July 1, 2025 July 1, 2028, pursuant to the provisions of the
21 Oklahoma Sunset Law, the State Board of Examiners of Psychologists.
22 The Board shall administer the provisions of the Psychologists
23 Licensing Act. The Board shall consist of seven (7) members
24 appointed by the Governor. Five members shall be psychologists from
